Pin Reference: G5LE-1 Relay (Omron)
=======================================
Library: Relay.kicad_sym
Type: SINGLE UNIT (all pins in one symbol - NOT multi-unit!)
Package: THT Relay_SPDT

IMPORTANT: This is a single-unit symbol. Place once with unit=1 and
all 5 pin UUIDs. Do NOT place as separate units.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
All pins (at angle=0):
---------------------------------------------------------------------
  Pin "5" local=(-5.08, 7.62)  -> offset (-5.08, -7.62) = UPPER LEFT  (coil-)
  Pin "2" local=(-5.08, -7.62) -> offset (-5.08, +7.62) = LOWER LEFT  (COM)
  Pin "4" local=(2.54, 7.62)   -> offset (2.54, -7.62)  = UPPER CENTER (NO)
  Pin "1" local=(5.08, -7.62)  -> offset (5.08, +7.62)  = LOWER RIGHT (coil+)
  Pin "3" local=(7.62, 7.62)   -> offset (7.62, -7.62)  = UPPER RIGHT (NC)

Coil connections: Pin 5 (coil-) at top-left, Pin 1 (coil+) at bottom-right
Switch contacts: Pin 2 (COM) at bottom-left, Pin 4 (NO) at top-center,
                 Pin 3 (NC) at top-right

Body bounding box: half=(10.16, 5.08), size=20.32 x 10.16mm
